response.overview: Jobe is resuscitated by Jonathan Walker. He wants Jobe to create a special computer chip that would connect all the computers in the world into one network, which Walker would control and use. But what Walker doesn't realize is a group of teenage hackers are on to him and out to stop his plan.
response.tagline: God made him simple. Science made him a god. Now, he wants revenge.
response.title: Lawnmower Man 2: Beyond Cyberspace

titles.title: El cortador de césped II: más allá del ciberespacio
